data.description: Very affordable two Unit Property, in very good condition, all owner occupied, 3 bedrooms on each apartment plus one up in the attic.  full unfinished basement. two cars garage. Book your appointment before is gone. Sold as is condition, The buyer is responsible to make the repairs on the Town of Cicero Inspection report, look under additional information for disclosures and report.
